.\" Manpage for loc
.TH man 1 "20 Mar 2018" "1.0" "loc man page"
.SH NAME
loc \- print lines of code recursively in a directory
.SH SYNOPSIS
loc directory
.SH DESCRIPTION
loc(Lines Of Code) will search recursively in the directory specified by the argument and counts the number of lines in each text file, and prints a summary of total lines of code, differenciating separate programming language if present. If code files have typical extensions(such as .c .java ...), loc will print a simple ASCII art showing the programming language.
.SH OPTIONS
Directory to search for must be specified
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
Dr-Noob(https://github.com/Dr-Noob)
